{"tid":124757,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共殖民政府：美國議會不應干預香港殖民地事務","createTime":"2017-02-18T01:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T05:03:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2638c572a1bad24b45d64ad675a49f1ad21dc19","tid":124757,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T01:29:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.news.gov.hk/tc/categories/admin/html/2017/02/20170217_221109.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcategories%2Fadmin%2Fhtml%2F2017%2F02%2F20170217_221109.shtml&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOe4S5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=ce19e5bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.news.gov.hk/tc/categories/admin/html/2017/02/20170217_221109.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n2017年02月17日<br />\n<br />\n香港殖民政府發表聲明，對美國議會在沒有證據證明支那機構曾跨境執法的情況下，動輒提出干預香港殖民地事務的法案草案，表示不能接受並極度遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n聲明回應傳媒報道美國參議員提出有關香港殖民地內部事務的法案草案，強調《基本法》確保香港殖民地在「一國兩制」方針下，依法實行「港人治港」和高度自治。<br />\n<br />\n香港殖民政府亦一直嚴格按照《基本法》、《香港人權法案條例》及其他法例保障香港市民的權利及自由。香港的法治精神、執法機關的嚴謹執法及獨立的司法制度，一向得到國際社會的高度評價和認同。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca02a7b38c53c2558bb92656a73176b5531b8f97","tid":124757,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:38:28.000Z","msg":"殖民地就=有權"},{"pid":"b4d2b75094688fdd656ae07244752c9ad55f3add","tid":124757,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:56:48.000Z","msg":"干預美國內政？"},{"pid":"de967c724ee2d612822a41262f35112dcb9e66fd","tid":124757,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>干預美國內政？</blockquote><br />\n 而家支共好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bac35d075800d40ff81f47fe3a520d75da942d4","tid":124757,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a